column5: Well my tickets for the spring fishing show arrived in my mail this morning....TJ i just wanted to say thankyou so much. Really i mean that you have no idea..........Now roll on saterday i cannot wait.
Wow talk about speedy delivery!!!  Hmmmmm....    Gerritt.

lol Gerrit actually i was thinking the same thing this morning when i opened them up. But seriously i cannot thank OFC enough for this. I think its awesome they do this ........letting members have an opportunity to win prizes.  Hell i am so excited you would think i was going to the bahamas or something.....lol
